      <title>习近平访问期间匈牙利计划与中国达成至少16项协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hungary-plans-at-least-16-agreements-with-china-during-xi-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利外交部长彼得·西雅尔托表示，匈牙利计划在习近平主席周三起为期三天的访问期间与中国签署至少 16 项协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hungary-plans-at-least-16-agreements-with-china-during-xi-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
